      <title>随着奈拉暴跌，大亨丹格特的糖业公司报告首次亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/aliko-dangote-s-sugar-firm-reports-first-loss-as-naira-plunges</link>
