    <item>
      <title>通过数据滴灌测试欧洲央行的金发姑娘通胀愿景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/ecb-s-goldilocks-inflation-vision-to-be-tested-by-data-drip-feed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行希望欧元区工资上涨足以推动经济扩张，而又不会重新引发通胀，但这一希望将受到缓慢发布的数据的考验，这些数据将决定何时可以安全地降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/ecb-s-goldilocks-inflation-vision-to-be-tested-by-data-drip-feed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
